{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"63321ccdbe","title":"刘少奇收到毛泽东9月14日信后给周恩来的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"34735bef4d","index":0,"year":1966,"month":9,"day":14,"articleId":"63321ccdbe","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"周恩来","id":"523bb79e8f","type":"人物"},{"name":"资产阶级反动路线","id":"70f02a0dc7","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"ed8d454915","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"2b7a0d2160","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"徐斌编著《风雨福禄居――刘少奇在“文革中的抗争”》（长春：吉林人民出版社，1998）第160页。"}],"contents":[{"id":"94f1b2e08f","type":"title","text":"刘少奇收到毛泽东9月14日信后给周恩来的信","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"ab64707603","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东在9月14日这一天给刘少奇写来一封短信：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c9f89ca2e1","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"30503e4983","type":"paragraph","text":"基本上写得很好，很严肃，特别后半段更好。建议以草案形式印发政治局、书记处、工作组长（领导干部）、北京市委、中央文化小组各同志讨论一下，提出意见，可能有些收获，然后酌加修改，再作报告，可能稳正一些，请酌定。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7336fcb8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇立即给周恩来写信：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"32714a8749","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a2d65e57d8","type":"paragraph","text":"我的检讨提纲，毛主席已经看过，并批了一段话，退还给我。现送上，请你看看。我赞成毛主席的意见，以草案形式印发政治局、书记处、工作组领导干部、北京市委、中央文化革命小组各同志讨论一下，并请他们提出意见，退还给我，然后酌加修改，再作报告。关于印发事，请你批办，请各同志在几天之内提出意见告我，给我以帮助。主席的批语也印发。如何？请你酌情安排。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0b098a51bc","type":"paragraph","text":"少奇同志：","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1fd301bbe1","type":"title","text":"刘少奇收到毛泽东9月14日信后给周恩来的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"436bf99e3e","type":"paragraph","text":"刘少奇立即给周恩来写信：","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5705fdc8e6","type":"paragraph","text":"恩来同志：","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c04e90460","type":"paragraph","text":"基本上写得很好，很严肃，特别后半段更好。建议以草案形式印发政治局、书记处、工作组长（领导干部）、北京市委、中央文化小组各同志讨论一下，提出意见，可能有些收获，然后酌加修改，再作报告，可能稳正一些，请酌定。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"73535abcff","type":"paragraph","text":"我的检讨提纲，毛主席已经看过，并批了一段话，退还给我。现送上，请你看看。我赞成毛主席的意见，以草案形式印发政治局、书记处、工作组领导干部、北京市委、中央文化革命小组各同志讨论一下，并请他们提出意见，退还给我，然后酌加修改，再作报告。关于印发事，请你批办，请各同志在几天之内提出意见告我，给我以帮助。主席的批语也印发。如何？请你酌情安排。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a78ee0c93a","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东在9月14日这一天给刘少奇写来一封短信：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"63321ccdbe","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}